==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Eight
<hw>Eight</hw> <pr>(⟦amac⟧t)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
number greater by a unit than seven; eight units or objects.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A symbol representing eight units, as 8 or
viii.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Eighteen</ent>⟦br⟧
